Title: Janky Candles
Description:
With new candle almost ready, now all need is to set up stall! Bring quality candle at good price to people! That Janky guarantee.

Only problem is not have stall. You talk to Bosh in Gun-dar-ghaz for me? He have everything we need.

May need barter, but you talk good! Make him give parts.

Meet you down there!
ObjectivesText: Acquire the parts Janky needs to build his stall in Gundargaz.
RewardText:
Good talking, $n. Make great merchant one day.

Like Janky!

Objectives.Text: Speak with Innkeeper Brax about Bosh's tab
Speak with Foreman Shalea about the construction
Speak to Machinist Valyka about the tools
Speak to Foreman Svart about the coal shipment
